{"tid":1292334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多賢黨入] JYP緊急公告多賢不上台 TWICE傷兵已經第二人","createTime":"2019-07-07T09:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T08:35:41.000Z","uid":74065,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1186753eeeb510fd2189e194034d62dabb6e0b","tid":1292334,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE再添傷兵，JYP娛樂在TWICE韓國官網緊急宣布成員多賢，因為身體不適，不會參加今（7）日的公演活動，由於2天前成員MINA才負傷缺席日本及韓國活動，多賢身體微恙再度引發粉絲憂心：「TWICE是不是太操了？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4218/d4218544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4218%2Fd4218544.jpg&h=0c429d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE多賢也宣布休養缺席。（圖／翻攝自TWICE臉書）<br />\n<br />\n根據JYP娛樂稍早公告，表示多賢因健康上的事由，「為了健康採取的措施，判斷必須要休息，無可避免地做出了不會出席的決定。」她本來將和團員在今天韓國時間下午4點到6點參加一場公演活動，加上MINA也於日前宣布負傷休養，今天的活動等於只有7人會出席，一下子少了2名成員，JYP娛樂也道歉：「對於期待演出的粉絲感到抱歉」。<br />\n<br />\n其實5日TWICE飛往日本時，多賢依舊上直播節目敬業表演，但粉絲間傳言她疑似生病、有吊點滴，似乎健康問題早就有徵兆。這也不是她首次因為健康因素缺席，去年4月底就因此無法登上音樂節目《Show!音樂中心》的舞台，也取消現身簽名會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4218/d4218549.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4218%2Fd4218549.jpg&h=974788da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE多賢5日正常飛往日本參加活動。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\n由於TWICE正在舉辦世界巡迴演唱會，13號就要在新加坡開唱，17號轉往美國洛杉磯、19號在墨西哥，月底還有2個美國都市的巡演行程要消化。聽聞TWICE傷兵不斷，粉絲心疼，「是不是太操了？」、「真的要好好休息，後面還有很多活動啊」、「希望其他人都好好的」等留言。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以話JYP對職員真係好好</span></strong></span><br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\nMina身體又出狀況！都飛日本了臨時取消上台...連韓國行程也影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1287862/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1287862/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9807100b029859146eddc79c67d7318a99e48645","tid":1292334,"uid":76115,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"係咪柯爛屎"},{"pid":"d8532fe6c78bacf2270856771d49f71d6747759a","tid":1292334,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:15:51.000Z","msg":"腎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c734aebeeaeb53d20d68fd05a89a8c9bb10d6818","tid":1292334,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"我瑜寶都唔知點算(｡ ́︿ ̀｡)"},{"pid":"60e150f9c873bd7f5337ec18191d1c79bf38d5a1","tid":1292334,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9807100b029859146eddc79c67d7318a99e48645","tid":1292334,"uid":76115,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"係咪柯爛屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"靚女唔會柯屎"},{"pid":"bbafe98287fccbf7cbd9aa10e20484324811d413","tid":1292334,"uid":19